to my question?

307
00:21:49,244 --> 00:21:51,181
Huh? Huh? No?

308
00:21:51,281 --> 00:21:52,344
No.

309
00:21:52,444 --> 00:21:53,544
Well, let's try that again.

310
00:21:53,644 --> 00:21:55,413
Come on. Can we think
of something fun

311
00:21:55,513 --> 00:21:56,828
that we want to do today?

312
