about crap like that.

482
00:29:37,843 --> 00:29:40,247
But weren't his eyes always bad?

483
00:29:40,347 --> 00:29:42,546
Mm, more or less.

484
00:29:42,645 --> 00:29:43,744
Well, if they're so strict,

485
00:29:43,844 --> 00:29:46,263
